{"tid":1368250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"五大訴求，缺一不可：切勿鍾情於「獨立調查委員會」","createTime":"2019-07-26T12:31:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T17:10:36.000Z","uid":131691,"like":143,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"f0e95da52b6615fed1a729a92525221332078894","tid":1368250,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:31:18.000Z","msg":"「獨立調查委員會」係政府最容易做嘅<br />\n所以亦都係最有可能，真係無計可施嘅時候，會妥協嘅一點訴求<br />\n搵個李家超，或者甚至局長祭旗<br />\n<br />\n但係如果香港人就咁就收貨，就真係萬劫不復<br />\n因爲背後令到須要「獨立調查委員會」嘅體制，依然係到<br />\n今次調查完，唔使幾耐，暴政又會返嚟殺香港人<br />\n而且唔會再有機會反抗，因爲「香港人已經收咗貨啦，政府已經讓咗步啦」<br />\n<br />\n所以，<br />\n就算727元朗嘅重點，係警黑合作<br />\n就算呢幾日因爲警黑合作，而逼到好多人支持「成立獨立調查委員會」呢個訴求<br />\n但係香港人一定唔可以就此罷休<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"8f805dc9d1cb5e6c9d8d2f9797f65fa512c91fe6","tid":1368250,"uid":181035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:32:04.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3f2b3d96847da4e1b69cc3f1d94dbf64e35578d","tid":1368250,"uid":105905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:32:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求!!!!<br />\n缺一不可</span>"},{"pid":"e32f97fc0834bfd477bc6ba32f9ba9fd5e848e12","tid":1368250,"uid":105905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:32:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f25d2d3f4b24df15dd576597b2d496259b775e6","tid":1368250,"uid":279650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:33:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6f802e9dd05d1b44d3fa74adaf8b0af5df65727d","tid":1368250,"uid":111934,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:34:17.000Z","msg":"起碼起碼<br />\n都要有真雙普選先好收貨"},{"pid":"ee00072004ff3593d08af7c806b969076e435be5","tid":1368250,"uid":52477,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:34:25.000Z","msg":"啱呀 可以嘅話唔好調查喇 直接顛覆啦"},{"pid":"543381fb832dbe02068e62a2c736195c4a2bdc8d","tid":1368250,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee00072004ff3593d08af7c806b969076e435be5","tid":1368250,"uid":52477,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:34:25.000Z","msg":"啱呀 可以嘅話唔好調查喇 直接顛覆啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:37:25.000Z","msg":"已經嗌緊時代革命<br />\n當口號嗌完都無反應，啲人就會自然實踐"},{"pid":"87af5a7ae6ae22a7f45651c9bcbe543b2dccc92b","tid":1368250,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:38:15.000Z","msg":"不要說「五大訴求」，試著說「警黑合作」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1367891\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1367891</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"aa383d464e29e1bf7af8bd007b50ceeab1aa9fb6","tid":1368250,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dis